Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:33.28,Poster Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:35.35,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.48,0:01:37.80,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:43.51,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Not often that you start\Na conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:44.52,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:48.15,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,What are you grinning for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:49.13,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:49.84,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Creepy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:51.25,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:53.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are those new hair ties?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:57.98,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Kariu-san and Tamarai-san \Ngave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:01:59.67,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,As thanks for the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.83,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like Hishiro-san's \Nstarting to change, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:09.39,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Arata-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.97,0:02:11.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,An! Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.83,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Hishiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:17.43,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, four-eyed braid girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.46,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I have a name. It's Onoya An.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:22.19,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Remember it already,\N Hishiro Chizuru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:25.76,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It is far too early to be that hyper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:29.30,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I have low blood pressure, \Nso honestly, I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.96,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, even Hishiro-san \Ngets jealous sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:37.12,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,But is that really caused \Nby low blood pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.42,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Onoya-san! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:45.54,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:46.48,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.04,0:02:48.77,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Hishiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:50.85,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,For the loud interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.81,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna borrow her for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.04,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.04,0:02:56.49,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,O-Ow! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.46,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:04.44,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's the first time\NI've seen you talking to Yoake-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.94,0:03:07.12,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:10.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo was in my class last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:11.25,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,"Ryo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:15.77,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, you call Yoake-kun "Ryo"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:16.64,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:18.58,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,He asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:23.07,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty close, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.34,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:28.18,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Don't jump to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:31.68,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She calls Oga "Kazu-kun" like he told her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.76,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:38.19,sign_5114_46_Ryo,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:38.19,sign_5122_47_Kazu_kun,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:35.29,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:38.19,sign_5161_49_Kaizaki_san,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:37.96,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't accept this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.62,0:03:41.33,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then call me Arata—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.08,0:03:45.88,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.81,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.47,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.75,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1)}Double Panic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:54.53,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,How old am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.74,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Summer vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.70,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You look super happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:04.99,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Damn straight I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:07.76,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,These long vacations are to be treasured!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.18,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even get that, young students?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.02,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Arata. You had to take\Nmake-ups after the finals, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.39,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Have you passed them yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.39,0:04:16.24,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:18.10,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:21.42,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll be doing make-ups \Nduring summer vacation, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.16,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Even during summer vacation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.33,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,So I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:28.66,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had to take one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:33.85,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been taking make-ups \Nthe entire first term...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.16,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,You reap what you sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.84,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be coming to prep for entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:40.28,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat lunch together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:45.14,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oga, you're going to some other college?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.57,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.57,0:04:49.82,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still considering just going on \Nto Aoba University,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:52.73,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like to keep my options open,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.64,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm gonna take the \NCenter Exam Prep Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.22,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:03.78,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, homeroom's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.95,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Oga-kun, Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:10.30,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,A big hand for our first-term class reps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.44,0:05:13.82,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:18.30,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yoake-san mentioned this high school \Nwas affiliated to a college.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.90,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Guess most of them go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:24.04,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.35,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,They get to be together in college, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:31.19,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,"Lucky them"? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.70,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:43.81,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,So, to celebrate successfully \Nsurviving the first term...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.32,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:47.36,Main Dialogue,All,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.70,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Again, how come we always \Nhave to drink at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:55.59,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Well, looking like this, \Nwe can't go out to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:58.02,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Can't even buy booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:06:02.54,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But here, we can get the lab to deliver it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:05.05,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,And we can expense it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:07.55,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Such horrible grown-ups!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.20,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:13.07,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to know your summer \Nvacation plans as soon as possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:14.82,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't have any, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:18.23,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're too busy taking make-ups \Nto even visit your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.19,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Can you pass before the vacation ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:24.07,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:28.28,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if you do go anywhere, \Nlet us know ahead of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:32.18,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a vacation, \Nbut we still have to observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:33.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:36.68,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,That said, Onoya and I will be \Njoining in summer school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:38.45,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,so we'll see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:39.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:42.20,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Part of our job is studying furiously
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:45.04,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,so we can convincingly act like students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:49.40,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,First Oga, now you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.40,0:06:51.55,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of ways to handle summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.56,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Speaking of Oga-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.94,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,He really hasn't noticed, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.76,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,How Kariu-san feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.70,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Unless the rest of us do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.70,0:07:05.82,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,those two will never get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.44,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.44,0:07:11.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We need to make Oga feel \Nsome danger, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.23,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:14.74,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Senpai, go after Kariu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.15,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,With your adult charm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:17.12,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:20.72,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,If another guy gets close to \NKariu-san and tempts her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:24.32,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,even Oga would have to feel {\i1}something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.09,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:29.59,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san is one thing,\Nbut how does Oga-kun feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:32.84,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really something we should be\Ngetting worked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.44,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We're all old enough
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:39.44,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,to know better than to toy \Nwith the hearts of children.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.74,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,What is this sadist talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:47.85,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,After all the time he's spent \Ntoying with my heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.85,0:07:48.86,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:50.74,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You drunkards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:54.26,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Kaizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:59.72,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping those who are \Nas innocent as Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.62,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no reason you couldn't \Nhave something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.50,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Get myself a high school girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.41,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason you couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:13.68,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,A one-year, limited edition of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:16.60,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.14,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,They'll forget you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.30,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:24.40,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to remind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.79,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Arata! Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:37.75,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.00,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda unusual to see you\Nbring lunch from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.00,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,The cafeteria's closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:47.15,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I make one for my dad every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.92,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,so I just double up during holidays.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:52.85,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You made that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:55.36,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I cook a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.68,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I seriously didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.47,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Falling for me yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Totally...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.76,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,So, how'd the make-ups go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.76,0:09:05.86,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I failed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.18,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:08.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:13.19,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san is one thing,\Nbut how does Oga-kun feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.02,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Oga...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:26.72,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard any rumors\Nabout your love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:27.28,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:29.00,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, not "hm."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:32.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You ever dated a girl before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:35.31,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No! Where'd this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.31,0:09:36.62,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Any ask you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.96,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Um... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:41.56,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,And you said no?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.54,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,But seriously, what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.82,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering \Nif there's anyone you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.84,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.49,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I like everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What kinda answer is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:01.82,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,My head's better than yours any day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:05.78,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We are clearly talking about love! Romance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:09.91,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look baffled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:12.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:16.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like, someone you always\Nfind yourself with, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.22,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a girl, a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:26.65,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,And you go, "She's interesting."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.19,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,"She's fun."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.49,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You can talk about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want anyone taking her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.24,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.70,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:42.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe go all the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:45.62,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I've never looked at anyone like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was speaking hypothetically.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.47,0:10:49.12,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Asking if you had anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.65,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:58.29,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Studying's important, \Nbut I think love is, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last summer of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.97,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precious time that won't come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:07.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Before you know it, you'll be \Nthe only single guy you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.60,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.24,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I self-destructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:18.24,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,My chest hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:21.28,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Arata...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:22.91,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.07,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,...ever done it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.61,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.93,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,like, kissed a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:34.67,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.34,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're dumb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:39.02,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's that got to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:40.41,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,But it's {\i1}you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:41.94,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't reject my very being!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:42.93,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:43.94,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,That's so naughty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:46.44,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a modern high school boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:47.28,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:47.96,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,English Pop Quiz - 50 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:57.49,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Studying's important, \Nbut I think love is, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.81,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last summer of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.98,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precious time that won't come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:06.67,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,"Won't come again"? That's every summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:07.79,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.50,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.86,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:20.04,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I've never looked at anyone like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.18,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:29.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Argh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.35,0:12:31.81,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up wasting\Nalmost the whole day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Vacation: Ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.90,0:12:38.19,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still a lot easier than \Nattending an exam school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.49,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You call this easy? You really know\Nhow to get on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:43.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:45.20,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:49.79,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:50.66,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.58,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:06.14,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's that new guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:08.89,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.47,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone finds out about ReLIFE,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.35,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,the experiment ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.31,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What's Kariu doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:19.07,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a student!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.35,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,And he's kinda scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:23.32,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,It's not some sort of hookup site thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kariu, of all people,\N would never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:31.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he's up to \Nanything that creepy, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:33.37,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to get her in his car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:36.25,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What now? He's kidnapping her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:39.50,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I really don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But what are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,This clearly isn't any kind of date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:47.22,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu's resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.56,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:01.52,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.74,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why did you just run out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.99,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Please, don't call my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.37,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me mixed up in this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.95,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.54,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:16.78,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,No! A friend from class!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.34,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:23.59,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Oga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.38,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Coming home from exam prep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.05,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:30.14,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:32.55,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.98,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,A friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.56,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:45.07,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,This girl's got a touch of heat stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.15,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to pass by.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:49.00,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Heat... stroke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.16,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,I asked if she wanted me\N to call an ambulance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.29,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,but she said it wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.29,0:14:57.25,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,So I took her somewhere cool \Nand got her a drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.21,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,and she's doing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.21,0:15:01.79,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty much what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:03.63,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,And given how hot it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.96,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't wanna let her walk off alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.30,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,so I offered to drop her at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.92,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,But obviously she doesn't want \Nto get into a strange man's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.68,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,We were at an impasse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:17.14,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Can I leave you with him, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:18.65,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.48,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.86,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Just 'cause you're young, \Ndon't take the heat lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.03,Main Dialogue,Kamioka,0000,0000,0000,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:26.40,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.16,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What a gentleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:35.91,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I heard all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:39.12,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like things are gonna work out,\N so I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.12,0:15:41.04,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Walk Kariu home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.88,0:15:43.21,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,He went home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.71,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.42,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:48.67,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.26,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.26,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.01,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oga...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:57.47,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:03.15,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for, uh, worrying about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.07,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:11.36,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You're being so sincere today\Nthat it's kinda weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:12.91,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.16,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Weird?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.74,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,You picked the worst timing to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.25,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.96,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I clearly messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:21.08,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:27.09,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why are you laughing\Nafter I hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.26,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,You're scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:31.96,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just thought, we're always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.80,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.39,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really. Glad you're enjoying yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:08.05,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering \Nif there's anyone you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.55,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want anyone taking her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.64,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:39.03,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last summer of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:41.08,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precious time that won't come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:43.21,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,A one-year, limited edition of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:46.96,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're an illusion. \NThey'll forget you, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:53.09,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do, Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:57.51,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in love with Kariu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.76,0:18:02.39,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.98,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,When I was walking Kariu to the station,\NI wanted to hold her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.48,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.61,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Stop giving me that look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:15.70,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't stop smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:16.66,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.95,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Oga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.33,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:23.07,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,you've gotta be a man and take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,There's a fireworks festival soon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:29.58,Poster Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Fireworks Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:29.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Invite her to it, and fess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.50,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Fess up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:34.21,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You mean tell Kariu I love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:35.63,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.26,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What else would you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.76,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,She'd punch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:40.09,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:46.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But are you okay with dawdling about? \NSomeone else might claim her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.36,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.57,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.95,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,A confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.60,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:02.27,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,When did you all get here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.00,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we thought you could use \Na young girl's point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:07.50,sign_27477_352_Young_girl_,,0000,0000,0000,,"Young" girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.75,sign_27513_353_Uselessly_dense,,0000,0000,0000,,Uselessly dense
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:09.96,sign_27543_354_Tag_along,,0000,0000,0000,,Tag-along
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.75,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I do wanna confess,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:15.21,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't know where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:19.05,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,An-chan, how would you like a boy \Nto confess his feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:23.76,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he puts his heart into it, \Nit really doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:24.97,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:26.73,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.73,0:19:29.64,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I have no experience with these things,\Nso I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.44,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:33.55,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Yoake-kun, how would you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.44,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You seem so grown-up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.32,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd make for a great reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:42.07,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done it, either. \NDon't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:43.53,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.04,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Arata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:49.12,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you lure all your girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:51.00,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You've had lots, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.54,0:19:54.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I did {\i1}not{\i0} say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:57.34,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,No, you're so relaxed around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.51,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You've known a lot of girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.18,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:07.39,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san has a lot of\N experience with women?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.51,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,How grown-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.02,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.31,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,We're in third year!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:16.30,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I apologize for being abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:17.82,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:21.19,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop smiling and help me out here,\N you support people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:25.91,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yoake-kun, surely you've asked \Nsomeone out or been asked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.70,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're eighteen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.37,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still seventeen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.20,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's beside the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.75,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,But I bet Arata-kun's \Npick-up lines are great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.75,Main Dialogue Top,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I really am abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:38.30,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta tell me! I need help here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:38.30,Main Dialogue Top,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I'm so abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:39.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.30,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.21,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:50.35,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll invite Kariu to \Nthe fireworks festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.52,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,...and confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:28.95,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu, are you free on the 10th?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:30.95,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna go to the\Nfireworks festival together?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:34.50,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.75,0:22:36.50,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Did he send it to the wrong person?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.75,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,No, it says "Kariu"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:39.70,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:43.94,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, I'd better see \Nwhat Honoka and Hishiro think...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:48.34,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Oga just invited me \Nto the fireworks festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.87,0:22:55.12,Italics Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, too! Sounds like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.87,0:22:57.56,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I got one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:00.33,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing homework \Nand studying all summer,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.33,0:23:02.58,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,so it'll be nice to take a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.52,0:23:07.46,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,He sent it to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.46,0:23:09.56,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I got all worked up for nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:13.44,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,But sure, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.94,0:23:16.62,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,That's just like Oga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.00,0:23:22.79,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}I got one, too.\NI've been doing homework and studying all summer,\Nso it'll be nice to take a breather.
