Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:22.79,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:24.88,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2500)}{\an9}Are you gonna wear a yukata, Hishiron?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:24.88,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2500)}{\an6}I don't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.79,0:23:24.88,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,2500)}{\an3}Then let's go shopping together!\NI was thinking of getting a new one myself.
