Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:27.72,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro, do you like green?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:30.93,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You like drab colors, Kaizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:33.82,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Drab? I guess I own a lot of dark colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:36.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I like bright colors, too. Red, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:40.05,Next Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,1)}Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:37.81,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:39.69,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What for?
